💐 Happy Mother's Day! 
I went out to an early breakfast. Took a nap! And baked cupcakes! In a little while, heading to my parent's for dinner. But first, I thought I'd share my MOTD with a shoutout to the beautiful new products from @itcosmetics 💐 They generously gifted me the 24 hour Superhero mascara and their No Tug shadow sticks! I used some shades from my Tom Ford Nude Dip in the crease and under eye. The #itcosmetics cream shadows were so pretty on my lids!  And this mascara is amazing!! No flaking or smudging!  Thank you to their wonderful PR team for always sending me the best goodies!

Thursday night I opened this perfectly timed PR gift from @renskincare 👌🏼💚 Usually, I'm red for at least 5 days! Today is the end of day 2 and 2 nights using Evercalm Overnight Recovery Balm. I'm barely red at all!  I actually went out to lunch with no makeup today! This balm is so good for repairing the skin barrier and helping settle down red angry skin!  Super impressed! Thank you Ren Skincare! 💚💚💚
